summary: This document is a summary of account balances and transactions for a Deutsche Bank account from January 1 to January 31, 2015. It details various debits and credits, including payroll fees and tax payments, and provides an overview of the account's financial activity during this period.
keyFacts: The account had a beginning balance of $8,801.98 on January 1, 2015.
A total of $200,000.00 was transferred into the account on January 5, 2015.
Multiple preauthorized debits were made for payroll fees and taxes throughout January.
The ending balance of the account as of January 31, 2015, was $176,626.67.
There were no overdraft fees or NSF return item fees for the statement period.
